snippet.title: Birth Trailer
snippet.description:
Birth is an adventure puzzle game about constructing a creature from spare bones & organs found around the city in order to quell your loneliness.

Solve physics-based puzzles & discover secrets in lovingly hand-drawn museums, bakeries, bookstores and more.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1889040/Birth/
